      </Heading>
      <p class="text-3xl md:text-xl leading-snug dark:text-gray-200">
        I'm all about keeping my digital life organized, and that means
        maintaining a pristine inbox! For the quickest way to get in touch, drop
        me a message at <a
          class="font-bold underline"
          href={`mailto:${email}`}
          >{email}</a
        > ‚ù§Ô∏è
      </p>
      <p class="text-3xl md:text-xl leading-snug dark:text-gray-200">
